Vol / Page:  182
Edition:
Quote:  The Kauri bug (called by the Maoris the [184] Kekereru), with its power of emitting a terrible ... smell when alarmed, has been ... fully dealt with ... <i>ibid.</i> The Kauri bug (Kekereru) ... has been so often and fully dealt with by writers.
